<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="N6945025R0003">
  <data key="d0">N6945025R0003</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">N6945025R0003 is the solicitation and resulting contract number referenced throughout the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Solicitation document outlining option line items for base operations support services, including pricing arrangements and references to attachments.&lt;SEP&gt;N6945025R0003 is the solicitation number for the Mayport BOS procurement.&lt;SEP&gt;N6945025R0003 is the contract document that incorporates various FAR and DFARS clauses and includes full text provisions on approvals, damages, and ordering.&lt;SEP&gt;N6945025R0003 is the contract or solicitation identifier referenced throughout the document sections.&lt;SEP&gt;N6945025R0003 is the solicitation number associated with the contract and referenced on multiple pages.&lt;SEP&gt;N6945025R0003 is the solicitation number associated with the evaluation preferences and contract clauses described.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bafeb026eba657c5147474a89dc0e6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
