</node>
<node id="Attachment J-0200000-17">
  <data key="d0">Attachment J-0200000-17</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment J-0200000-17 is an Excel spreadsheet containing exhibit line item numbers for pricing CLINs across base and option periods.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment containing worksheets for exhibit line item numbers and sub-ELINs used in pricing various option periods, with instructions to use the most current version and check amendments.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment J-0200000-17 provides Exhibit Line Item Numbers used in the ELIN pricing spreadsheet.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795800</data>
</node>
<node id="Performance Work Statement">
  <data key="d0">Performance Work Statement</data>
  <data key="d1">statement_of_work</data>
  <data key="d2">Performance Work Statement outlines the service requirements, deliverables, and applicable attachments for the base operations support contract.&lt;SEP&gt;The Performance Work Statement describes requirements for relevant projects in evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;Document specifying performance-based requirements for recurring and non-recurring base operations support services at specified locations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Performance Work Statement outlines services similar in size, scope, and complexity for relevant project evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Performance Work Statement contains performance objectives that offerors should not merely parrot in proposals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795800</data>
</node>
