  <data key="d0">Water Annex</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Specific annex requiring recurring base operations support services as part of option line items.&lt;SEP&gt;Water Annex specifies recurring base operations support services for water in the base period and option periods, priced under separate CLINs.</data>
