  <data key="d0">Firm Fixed Price</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Pricing arrangement applied to all option line items for the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Firm Fixed Price is the pricing structure for recurring work in the base period and option periods of the contract.</data>
