<node id="Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island">
  <data key="d0">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is another site for work performance, located in Jacksonville, Florida.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is located in Jacksonville, Florida and primarily hosts custodial, pest control, integrated solid waste management, and grounds maintenance services.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps support facility in Jacksonville, Florida, designated for base operations support services.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island (MCSF-BI) is a military facility site referenced in facility inventories, site maps, investment data, and system-specific attachments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-729293c3f8703afb2cb5e31cb6ff90dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb</data>
