  <data key="d0">Facilities Support Services</data>
  <data key="d1">strategic_theme</data>
  <data key="d2">Facilities Support Services is the core service category for the acquisition, classified under NAICS 561210 and involving inventories of utilities, maintenance, and environmental systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795801</data>
