<node id="NAVFAC">
  <data key="d0">NAVFAC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">NAVFAC establishes command-wide small business subcontracting targets based on a percentage of total planned subcontract dollars.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC operates the Contractor Incident Reporting System for safety data.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC provides command-wide small business subcontracting targets including 40% for Small Business.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC provides Maximo Data critical to government processes.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC is the Naval Facilities Engineering Systems Command, which issues instructions on crane and railroad trackage and provides Maximo asset management systems and naming conventions referenced in attachments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6277b393cb9cf1d4f0f247c35b0fffa1</data>
