<node id="Attachment JM-2">
  <data key="d0">Attachment JM-2</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment JM-2 is the Small Business Utilization and Participation factor for consistency with the subcontracting plan.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment JM-2 is used to demonstrate historical small business utilization for projects under Factor 1 Corporate Experience.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment JM-2 contains commitments offered in the Small Business Utilization and Participation factor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
