  <data key="d5">1759795802</data>
</node>
<node id="Federal Acquisition Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Federal Acquisition Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Federal Acquisition Regulation governs the solicitation, including definitions of service contracts under FAR 37.101 and clauses like FAR 52.222-43 and FAR 52.222-32.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Acquisition Regulation governs cost principles, clauses, and contract administration, with supplements applicable to indirect costs and small business representations.&lt;SEP&gt;Federal Acquisition Regulation (48 CFR Chapter 1) is the regulatory framework referenced in clauses for deviations and incorporations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Acquisition Regulation provides clauses incorporated by reference or full text in the solicitation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bafeb026eba657c5147474a89dc0e6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795802</data>
</node>
<node id="Defense Federal Acquisition Regulation Supplement">
  <data key="d0">Defense Federal Acquisition Regulation Supplement</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Defense Federal Acquisition Regulation Supplement includes clauses for DoD-specific requirements in the solicitation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795802</data>
</node>
<node id="Section B">
  <data key="d0">Section B</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">Section B details supplies or services and prices or costs, including contract line item numbers, pricing structure, maximum not-to-exceed values, and minimum guarantees.&lt;SEP&gt;Section B contains pricing information submitted within the proposal for evaluation of inconsistencies.&lt;SEP&gt;Section B contains the contract's pre-priced line items, supported by Section J ELINs, used for FedMall orders and GCPC purchases.&lt;SEP&gt;Section B requires completion for pricing submittal in the solicitation.&lt;SEP&gt;Section B contains line items referenced in the pricing spreadsheet data for the price proposal.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795802</data>
</node>
<node id="Section J">
  <data key="d0">Section J</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">Section J includes the ELIN attachment used for evaluating proposal pricing inconsistencies.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J is the List of Attachments that includes documents, exhibits, and other attachments posted on the SAM website at https://sam.gov/ with the solicitation, covering acquisition and technical documents.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J provides ELINs that support the Unit Price Tasks in Section B for ordering via FedMall.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J of Annex 1700000 specifies transportation equipment maintenance and repair time frames.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J includes the Exhibit Line Item Number Pricing Attachment for pricing evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795803</data>
</node>
