  <data key="d0">Independent Government Estimate</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Independent Government Estimate is used in price evaluation comparisons with proposed prices and historical information.&lt;SEP&gt;The Independent Government Estimate is compared to proposed prices to ensure reasonableness.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
