  <data key="d0">Port Operations</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Port Operations (0600000) is a technical annex similar to RFP requirements, required for relevant project demonstration.&lt;SEP&gt;Port Operations under code 0600000 is similar to the RFP requirements for relevant project evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
