<node id="Facility Investment">
  <data key="d0">Facility Investment</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Facility Investment (1502000) includes completion of service orders, HVAC systems maintenance, fire protection systems maintenance, and two other facility investment items, required for relevant project demonstration.&lt;SEP&gt;Facility Investment under code 1502000 includes service orders, HVAC systems maintenance and repairs, fire protection systems maintenance and repairs, and at least two other items for relevance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
