<node id="Water">
  <data key="d0">Water</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Water (1606000) includes raw water supply, water treatment plant, distribution system operation, laboratory testing, maintenance, and repairs, similar to RFP requirements, required for relevant project demonstration.&lt;SEP&gt;Water under code 1606000 is part of the scope for determining relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
