  <data key="d0">52.215-1</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.215-1 is a clause titled Instructions to Offerors -- Competitive Acquisition, modified for all or none offers and referenced for proposal receipt provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795806</data>
</node>
<node id="52.208-9">
  <data key="d0">52.208-9</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.208-9 is a clause addressing Contractor Use of Mandatory Sources of Supply, requiring certain supplies from nonprofit agencies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795806</data>
</node>
<node id="252.209-7002">
  <data key="d0">252.209-7002</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">252.209-7002 is a representation titled Disclosure of Ownership or Control by a Foreign Government, applicable as indicated by the Contracting Officer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795806</data>
</node>
