  <data key="d1">submission_instruction</data>
  <data key="d2">The Responsibility Determination requires submission of specific documents including SF-33, financial statements, and team information in a binder with two copies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
