  <data key="d0">NAVFAC Maximo Data</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">NAVFAC Maximo Data is critical for government planning, programming, and budgeting, requiring maintenance of Service Provider, Asset, Specification, and Characteristic Meter Reading data fields throughout the Performance Work Statement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795812</data>
