  <data key="d0">Transportation Equipment</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Transportation Equipment must be maintained and repaired within specified time frames with minimal allowable downtime, as per Annex 1700000 Sections C and J.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795812</data>
</node>
<node id="Unit Price Labor (UPL)">
  <data key="d0">Unit Price Labor (UPL)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Unit Price Labor (UPL) requires a rate for one hour of work-in-place for work over Limits of Liability and other over-and-above work, encompassing all applicable costs including subcontracted work, without post-award renegotiation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795812</data>
</node>
<node id="Risk Mitigation">
  <data key="d0">Risk Mitigation</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Risk Mitigation involves practical contingency plans to address shortages of materials, equipment, and workers, including licensed, certified, and security-cleared personnel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759795812</data>
</node>
